21:31.867 --> 21:34.068
I love you.
Straight home after school.

21:34.070 --> 21:36.003
You know the route.
Subway, two stops.

21:36.005 --> 21:37.404
- Okay.
- Love you. Bye.

21:37.406 --> 21:39.141
Come on, let's go.

21:40.209 --> 21:41.676
Bye!

22:23.052 --> 22:24.885
So where do we start?

22:24.887 --> 22:28.822
Yeah, we start when you
get those dishes washed.

22:28.824 --> 22:30.924
I need this clean.

22:30.926 --> 22:32.725
Right now, come on!
Let's go!

22:32.727 --> 22:34.928
We have a lot to do, you know.

22:34.930 --> 22:35.898
Oh, man.

22:46.942 --> 22:47.709
Put it there.

23:06.162 --> 23:07.263
Sorry.

23:11.967 --> 23:13.267
<i>Co-op kitchen, day two.</i>

23:13.269 --> 23:15.035
<i>Sao Paulo meets Harlem prep.</i>

23:15.037 --> 23:19.806
<i>And I met lots of flies,
garbage and dirty dishes.</i>

23:19.808 --> 23:20.841
<i>Good start.</i>

23:45.534 --> 23:47.367
<i>Co-op kitchen, day three.</i>

23:47.369 --> 23:51.305
